Redis
- Open source, single threaded, in-memory database, latest version 4.0
- Data structures - string, list, set, sorted set, hash, bitmap
- Real time application - > restrict user to login lessthan 3 times in an hour(using time to live)
- Consumption based pay-> Pay as you go: <user id> usage 20 <user id> cost 40
- we can make the data persistent by writing the content on file
- Pub/Sub is used to message passing with n channels and n clients
- Master/Slave to make the data high-availability, failover